斯汀表示，吹牛老爹的指控并未影响《Every Breath You Take》：“这仍然是我的歌” https://www.nme.com/news/music/sting-says-diddy-allegations-have-not-tainted-every-breath-you-take-its-still-my-song-3811765?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=刺痛说迪迪指控没有污染你的每一次呼吸Surej SinghTue, 12 Nov 2024 05:39:07 +0000 Music NewsNewsRapRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3811765 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位名誉扫地的说唱歌手在“我会想念你”中采样了警察歌曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sting-says-diddy-allegations-have-not-tainted-every-breath-you-take-its-still-my-song-3811765">斯汀的帖子称吹牛老爹的指控并未影响《Every Breath You Take》：“这仍然是我的歌”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sting-diddy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/diddy">“吹牛老爹”肖恩·库姆斯</a>受到众多指控后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sting">斯汀</a>透露了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-police">警察乐队</a>《你的每一次呼吸》遗产的看法。</p><p> 1983年，The Police 发行了排行榜冠军单曲《Every Breath You Take》。 1997 年，吹牛老爹在自己发行的专辑《I&#39;ll Be Missing You》中采样了这首歌。现在，迪迪面临<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-charged-with-sex-trafficking-racketeering-and-transporting-for-prostitution-3794598">性交易、敲诈勒索和运送卖淫的指控</a>，斯汀分享了他对这位名誉扫地的说唱歌手样本的看法。 </p><figure id="attachment_3796021" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3796021" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3796021" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/sting@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3796021" class="wp-caption-text">斯汀现场表演。图片来源：Jeremychanphotography/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在接受《 <a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2024-11-11/sting-trio-tour-the-police-billy-joel-paul-simon-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>洛杉矶时报》</em></a>最新采访时，当被问及他是否认为警方的袭击事件受到了迪迪封面的污染时，斯汀回答道：“不。我的意思是，我不知道[和迪迪]发生了什么事。但这对我来说根本没有玷污这首歌。这仍然是我的歌。”</p><p>去年，吹牛老爹表示，他被迫在余生中每天向斯汀支付 4,020 英镑（5,000 美元）的样品费。不过，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-says-he-was-joking-about-being-forced-to-pay-sting-5000-a-day-for-the-rest-of-his-life-3427451">很快就收回了这一言论</a>，称自己“在开玩笑！”这才叫搞笑啊！我和@OfficialSting 已经是很久的朋友了！他从来没有因为《想念你》而向我收取每天 3,000 美元或 5,000 美元的费用。他可能每天从历史上最伟大的歌曲之一中赚到超过 5000 美元。”</p><p> Diddy于9月份首次被捕，并被指控犯有性贩运、运送卖淫等罪名。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-denied-bail-in-sex-trafficking-racketeering-case-3794666">他在提供 5000 万美元（3840 万英镑）保释金后被拒绝保释</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/p-diddy-reportedly-placed-on-suicide-watch-while-awaiting-trial-for-sex-crimes-3795772">据报道在等待审判期间他被置于自杀监视之下</a>。此后，该艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-appeals-bail-promises-no-women-and-drug-testing-3798498">对保释被拒绝提出上诉</a>。他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddys-sex-trafficking-trial-date-set-for-2025-3801704">审判日期定于 2025 年 5 月 5 日</a>。</p><p>他仍被联邦拘留在纽约市布鲁克林大都会拘留中心。库姆斯预计将于 12 月 18 日出庭。据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/sean-diddy-combs-sex-abuse-trial-date-1235129736/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>报道，如果罪名成立，他可能面临最高 15 年的监禁。 </p><figure id="attachment_3807467" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3807467" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3807467" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit.jpg" alt="肖恩·“老爹”库姆斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SeanDiddyCombs-lawsuit-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3807467" class="wp-caption-text">肖恩·“老爹”库姆斯。图片来源：威廉姆斯王子/WireImage/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>继最近指控吹牛<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-accused-of-sexually-assaulting-and-drugging-10-year-old-boy-3807367">老爹对一名 10 岁男孩进行性侵犯和下药</a>后，库姆斯的律师否认了最新一波指控，并批评了托尼·布兹比（Tony Buzbee）——这位律师目前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/120-people-are-working-on-new-lawsuits-against-diddy-for-sexual-abuse-including-25-minors-3798823">正在与 120 人合作，这些人对库姆斯提出了新的指控。耻辱的说唱大亨</a>——在一份声明中（通过<a href="https://www.complex.com/music/a/jose-martinez/diddy-accused-of-sexually-assaulting-10-year-old-boy-new-lawsuit" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Complex</em></a> ）。</p><p> “先生。库姆斯和他的法律团队对事实和司法程序的公正性充满信心。在法庭上，真相将占上风：库姆斯先生从未性侵犯或贩卖过任何人——男人或女人，成年人或未成年人。” </p><figure id="attachment_3801705" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3801705" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3801705" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sean-diddy-combs@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sean-diddy-combs@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sean-diddy-combs@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sean-diddy-combs@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sean-diddy-combs@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sean-diddy-combs@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sean-diddy-combs@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3801705" class="wp-caption-text">肖恩·“老爹”库姆斯。图片来源：杰夫·克拉维茨/FilmMagic</figcaption></figure><p>在其他新闻中，本月早些时候，一名匿名起诉迪迪强奸的妇女被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judge-rules-diddy-accuser-must-reveal-her-name-or-rape-case-will-be-thrown-out-3808917">告知，她必须透露自己的姓名，否则她的诉讼将被驳回</a>。法官要求 Jane Doe 在 11 月 13 日之前以自己的名义提出申诉，“否则此案将被驳回”。她说，无名氏的律师没有提供足够的证据来证明她的身份会造成精神伤害，并表示“公开羞辱”的前景还不够。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-accused-of-sexually-assaulting-and-drugging-10-year-old-boy-3807367"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><div class="lazyload-wrapper "><div class="sc-60597ed9-0 bZsoAc connatix-ad"><div id="connatix-container-0"><p><strong>如需有关英国性骚扰、侵犯和强奸的更多帮助、建议或更多信息，请访问<a href="http://rapecrisis.org.uk/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">强奸危机慈善网站</a>。在美国，请访问<a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RAINN</a> 。</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sting-says-diddy-allegations-have-not-tainted-every-breath-you-take-its-still-my-song-3811765">斯汀的帖子称吹牛老爹的指控并未影响《Every Breath You Take》：“这仍然是我的歌”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
乔纳斯兄弟 (Jonas Brothers) 翻唱 One Direction 的《Night Changes》以纪念利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) https://www.nme.com/news/music/jonas-brothers-honour-liam-payne-with-cover-of-one-directions-night-changes-3811750?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jonas-brothers-荣誉利亚姆佩恩与单向夜间变化封面Surej SinghTue, 12 Nov 2024 04:32:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3811750 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> One Direction 歌手于 10 月 16 日去世，享年 31 岁</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jonas-brothers-honour-liam-payne-with-cover-of-one-directions-night-changes-3811750">乔纳斯兄弟 (Jonas Brothers) 为利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) 翻唱 One Direction 的《Night Changes》而向 Liam Payne 致敬的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/jonas-brothers-liam-payne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jonas-brothers">乔纳斯兄弟</a>翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>的《Night Changes》，向已故的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">Liam Payne</a>致敬 - 请观看下面的封面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2024：单向明星帮助引发了流行现象</a></strong></li></ul><p>佩恩于10月16日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">从阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店三楼阳台坠落身亡，</a>年仅31岁。阿根廷检察官办公室随后表示，他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-cause-of-death-and-details-of-hotel-room-in-disarray-revealed-3803859">死因是多处外伤和内外出血</a>。</p><p> 11 月 10 日，兄弟三人组在加利福尼亚州演出时，以温柔翻唱 One Direction 的《Night Changes》向 Payne 致敬。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-jonas">尼克·乔纳斯（Nick Jonas）</a>拉开了这首歌的序幕，他演唱了第一节，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joe-jonas">乔加</a>入了第二节。两人轮流唱到歌曲结束，让观众自己唱出最后的歌词。</p><p>观看下面封面的粉丝镜头。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="夜晚的变化 - 乔纳斯兄弟" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/up1P3yy0KUs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这位单向明星去世后，初步毒理学测试显示，佩恩<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-payne-reportedly-had-pink-cocaine-and-other-substances-in-his-system-at-time-of-death-3804922">在从阳台坠落致死时，体内含有粉红色可卡因和其他几种物质</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-payne-had-cocaine-alcohol-and-antidepressants-in-his-system-at-time-of-death-toxicology-report-shows-3810966">最近的一份毒理学报告证实，</a>他死时体内含有可卡因、酒精和抗抑郁药物。</p><p>上周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/police-arrest-two-people-in-connection-with-death-of-liam-payne-3810706">三人因与他的死亡有关而受到指控，</a>但当时没有透露他们的名字。昨天（11月10日），据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/suspect-in-liam-payne-death-investigation-breaks-silence-3811500">，其中一名嫌疑人Braian Nahuel Paiz打破了对此事的沉默</a>。</p><p>他承认在这位已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">单向</a>歌手去世前两次见过他，并承认自己吸毒。然而，他坚称自己从未向利亚姆·佩恩提供毒品，也从未接受过他的任何金钱。</p><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rita-ora">丽塔·奥拉 (Rita Ora)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rita-ora-pays-emotional-tribute-to-liam-payne-at-2024-mtv-emas-he-left-such-a-mark-on-this-world-3811398">在昨晚（11 月 10 日）主持 2024 年 MTV EMA 时向佩恩表达了深切的敬意</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3810715" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3810715" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3810715" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/liam-payne-hania-lassen-1.jpg" alt="利亚姆·佩恩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/liam-payne-hania-lassen-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/liam-payne-hania-lassen-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/liam-payne-hania-lassen-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/liam-payne-hania-lassen-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/liam-payne-hania-lassen-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/liam-payne-hania-lassen-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3810715" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩.图片来源：Hania Lessen/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>颁奖期间，她在曼彻斯特 Co-op Live Arena 的舞台上发表讲话，她说：“我只是想花点时间记住我们非常非常亲爱的人。我们最近失去了他，他是 MTV 世界和我的世界的重要组成部分，我想你们家里以及今晚在座的每个人也有很多这样的人。</p><p> “利亚姆·佩恩是我认识的最善良的人之一。你知道，我们有很多方式来谈论向他致敬，但我认为有时只是简单地说就足够了。”</p><p> “他有一颗最伟大的心，他总是第一个尽其所能提供帮助的人，他给他走进的每个房间带来了如此多的欢乐，他在这个世界上留下了如此深刻的印记，”她继续说道。声音开始破裂。</p><p>现已解散的 One Direction 乐队的所有四名幸存成员—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/harry-styles-remembers-liam-payne-in-tribute-post-it-was-an-honour-to-be-alongside-him-3803922">哈里·斯泰尔斯 (Harry Styles)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/zayn-malik-postpones-us-tour-over-heartbreaking-loss-of-liam-payne-3804342">泽恩·马利克 (Zayn Malik)</a> 、路易斯·汤姆林森 (Louis Tomlinson) 和尼尔·霍兰 (Niall Horan)—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-speak-out-on-the-death-of-liam-payne-were-completely-devastated-3803904">此后都向佩恩表达了自己的敬意，并发表了一份集体声明</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jonas-brothers-honour-liam-payne-with-cover-of-one-directions-night-changes-3811750">乔纳斯兄弟 (Jonas Brothers) 为利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne) 翻唱 One Direction 的《Night Changes》而向 Liam Payne 致敬的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
