800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791888" class="wp-caption-text">杰克·怀特 (Jack White) 将于 2024 年 6 月演出。图片来源：Scott Legato/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>然而，现在， <a href="https://consequence.net/2024/11/the-white-stripes-withdraw-lawsuit-against-donald-trump/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Consequence</em></a>报道称，乐队已要求“不带偏见”地驳回这些索赔，这将使他们能够在未来重新提起另一项诉讼（如果他们选择这样做）。</p><p>该诉讼被驳回是杰克·怀特长期以来公开表现出对特朗普的蔑视的最新进展。在提起诉讼后，怀特于十月对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-white-to-fascist-donald-trump-youre-gonna-lose-michigan-bigly-you-wanna-be-dictator-orange-clown-3801886">即将上任的总统在底特律发表演讲时侮辱底特律进行了猛烈抨击</a>。特朗普曾一度以这座城市为例，说明如果他的对手副总统<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡马拉·哈里斯</a>继续赢得选举，这个国家将会发生什么。 “这将像底特律一样，”他说。 “如果她是你们的总统，我们整个国家最终都会像底特律一样。你的手上将会一片混乱。” </p><figure id="attachment_3802996" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3802996" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3802996" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Trump@2000x1270.jpg" alt="美国共和党总统候选人、前总统唐纳德·特朗普在竞选集会上跳舞" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Trump@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Trump@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Trump@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Trump@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Trump@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Trump@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attach